        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n@Pam, @Jorge and @Liam, here is the general status for the migration POJOs from policy/drools-application to policy/models:\n\n1. mirgrate model-impl from policy/drools-application to policy/models \n\thttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/83211/ -- Merged\n2. mirgrate actors from policy/drools-application to policy/models \n\thttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/83679/ -- Merged\n3. replace model-impl and actors dependencies in policy/drools-application by policy/models. \n\thttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/83967/ -- Review\n\thttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/84188/ -- Review\n4. replace model-impl and actors dependencies in policy/engine by policy/models.\n\thttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/84188/ -- Review\n5. mirgrate simulators from policy/drools-application to policy/models \n\thttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/84063/ -- Review\n6. mirgrate policy-yaml from policy/drools-application to policy/models\n\thttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/84066/ -- Review",
